# Mork Matters — environment variables
#
# Both are OPTIONAL. With no Supabase config the app runs fully in "guest mode"
# using localStorage for stats, answered-question history, and a local
# leaderboard. Add these to enable cloud accounts, cross-device saves, and the
# global live leaderboard.
#
# Find these in your Supabase project: Settings -> API.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-publishable-anon-key
